name: "Cherry Blossoms" By Sunny Crittenden
description: "Cherry Blossoms" was created in May 2020. It was the 2nd piece the artist ever created on her iPad inherited from her husband, with a 2nd hand Apple Pencil donated by a patron, using Procreate, and was the first of her signature SunnyGrrrls to be drawn digitally. "Cherry Blossoms" is essentially SunnyGrrrls' digital genesis.
